      "type": "text",
      "text": "Producers publish one notify.<ws> event with the resolved recipient_user_id; only the notification service\nknows prefs, persistence, in-app push (Redis -> SSE), and the email channel. Email failures retry -> notify.email.dlq;\nin-app delivery is never blocked by email (FR-032–FR-036).",
      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Producers publish one notify.<ws> event with the resolved recipient_user_id; only the notification service\nknows prefs, persistence, in-app push (Redis -> SSE), and the email channel. Email failures retry -> notify.email.dlq;\nin-app delivery is never blocked by email (FR-032–FR-036).",
